{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446800/extras/Welcome_To_Space_Orcs_Brawl.png?t=1740039730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready for chaotic, couch-multiplayer mayhem! Pilot wacky, battle-hardened space ships, each with their own wild abilities, and fight for glory in explosive arena combat. It\u2019s time to brawl\u2014who will rule the arena?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446800/extras/Seq_8.gif?t=1740039730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446800/extras/7_Crazy_Characters.png?t=1740039730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pick from a lineup of 7 unique  brawlers, each with their own look, personality, and special powers. Whether you\u2019re zipping around as Doc Croc or befuddle enemies with the tricky Brain Gang CEO, every ship brings a new way to play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446800/extras/Seq_2.gif?t=1740039730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446800/extras/Battle_Across_Wild_Arenas.png?t=1740039730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From asteroid belts to junkyard warzones, no two arenas are the same! Dodge hazards, master the terrain, and use the environment to your advantage as you battle for domination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446800/extras/Seq_7.gif?t=1740039730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446800/extras/Multiple_Game_Modes.png?t=1740039730\" />Mix things up with various action-packed game modes! Whether you're brawling for survival in random death match, assisting in team battles, or battling in crazy custom matches, there's always a new way to play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446800/extras/Seq_3.gif?t=1740039730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446800/extras/Local_Multiplayer.png?t=1740039730\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grab your friends and jump into fast-paced local multiplayer! Play side by side, pull off crazy stunts, and send your rivals crashing into the abyss. No online lag\u2014just pure, old-school brawling fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446800/extras/Seq_6.gif?t=1740039730\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3446800?t=1740039730","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446800/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740039730","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446800/c86ecf898af9bcf19c51d6a4344eabfe08be708f/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740039730","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446800/c86ecf898af9bcf19c51d6a4344eabfe08be708f/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740039730","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Workshop","id":30},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Includes level editor","id":17},{"descript